---
// Static page — no data fetching needed
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>About — Pokédex</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
      body { font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif; background: #0a0a0f; color: #f0f0f5; min-height: 100vh; overflow-x: hidden; }

      body::before, body::after {
        content: ''; position: fixed; border-radius: 50%;
        filter: blur(140px); pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
      }
      body::before {
        width: 600px; height: 600px;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(249,115,22,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
        top: -200px; right: -100px;
      }
      body::after {
        width: 500px; height: 500px;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(139,92,246,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
        bottom: -150px; left: -100px;
      }

      nav {
        position: relative; z-index: 10;
        display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
        padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
        background: rgba(10,10,15,0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      }
      nav a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); text-decoration: none; margin-left: 2rem; transition: color 0.2s; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; }
      nav a:hover { color: #f97316; }
      .logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #f97316; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }

      main { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 5rem 2rem 4rem; }

      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.25rem); font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.1;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.6) 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;
      }
      h1 em {
        font-style: normal;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316 0%, #fb923c 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;
      }

      .lead { font-size: 1.05rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-bottom: 3.5rem; line-height: 1.75; max-width: 600px; }

      .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }

      .card {
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
        border-radius: 18px; padding: 1.5rem; backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
      }
      .card:hover { border-color: rgba(249,115,22,0.25); transform: translateY(-2px); }
      .card-icon { font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.85rem; }
      .card h2 { font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; color: #f97316; font-weight: 800; }
      .card p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); line-height: 1.65; }

      .cta { text-align: center; }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316 0%, #ea6c00 100%);
        color: white; padding: 0.9rem 2.25rem; border-radius: 12px;
        text-decoration: none; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1rem;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(249,115,22,0.3);
        transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
      }
      .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(249,115,22,0.4); }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav>
      <span class="logo">Pokédex</span>
      <div>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/pokedex">Pokédex</a>
        <a href="/ai-generator">AI Generator</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <main>
      <h1>The <em>Pokémon</em> World</h1>
      <p class="lead">Pokémon are creatures of all shapes and sizes who live in the wild or alongside humans. There are currently over 1000 known species, each with unique abilities, types, and stats.</p>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">🔥</div>
          <h2>18 Types</h2>
          <p>Every Pokémon has one or two types — Fire, Water, Grass, Electric, and 14 more. Types determine strengths and weaknesses in battle.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">🌍</div>
          <h2>9 Generations</h2>
          <p>New Pokémon are introduced with each game generation, starting with 151 original species in Generation I (1996) up to 1025+ today.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">📊</div>
          <h2>6 Base Stats</h2>
          <p>Each Pokémon has HP, Attack, Defense, Special Attack, Special Defense, and Speed — determining performance in battle.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">⚡</div>
          <h2>PokéAPI</h2>
          <p>This Pokédex is powered by PokéAPI — a free, open RESTful API serving over 2.5 billion calls per month with data on every Pokémon.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="cta">
        <a href="/pokedex" class="btn">Explore the Pokédex</a>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
